=========================================
RH ENTERPRISE - SMART CATEGORY LOGIC
=========================================

PURPOSE:
--------
Category page automatically decide karega ki:
- Subcategory dikhani hai
- Product listing dikhani hai
- Ya direct product page open karna hai

-----------------------------------------
MAIN DECISION FLOW
-----------------------------------------

STEP 1:
Check karo — kya is category ke andar subcategories hain?

IF subcategories exist:
    → Show subcategories (category view)

ELSE:
    → Check products inside category

        IF exactly 1 product:
            → Redirect to product detail page

        IF more than 1 product:
            → Show product listing grid

        IF no product:
            → Show "No subcategories or products found"

-----------------------------------------
PSEUDO CODE
-----------------------------------------

IF has_subcategories:
    show_subcategories()

ELSE:
    IF product_count == 1:
        redirect_to_product()

    ELSE IF product_count > 1:
        show_product_listing()

    ELSE:
        show_empty_message()

-----------------------------------------
WHY THIS LOGIC IS IMPORTANT
-----------------------------------------

• Unlimited category depth supported
• Mixed structure supported (category + product)
• No useless empty pages
• Better user experience
• Professional CMS architecture
• Works like Amazon / Flipkart category structure

-----------------------------------------
EXAMPLE STRUCTURE
-----------------------------------------

TATA
 ├── Clothing
 │     ├── Jeans (Product)
 │     └── Pants (Product)
 │
 └── Motors
       ├── Car
       │     ├── Nexon (Product)
       │     └── Safari (Product)
       │
       └── Truck

Flow Behaviour:

TATA → Show Clothing & Motors
Clothing → Show Jeans & Pants
Motors → Show Car & Truck
Car → Show Nexon & Safari
Truck → 
    IF 1 product → direct open product page
    IF multiple → show listing
    IF none → show empty message


